y/b/astronomy/archive/2019/02/25/astro-stuff-galore-at-the-swap-and-sell.aspx"><img src="http://cs.astronomy.com/resized-image.ashx/__size/300x0/__key/communityserver-blogs-components-weblogfiles/00-00-00-00-51-Star+parties/6560.SAS-2019-01.jpg" alt=""></a></div><div><a href="http://cs.astronomy.com/asy/b/astronomy/archive/2019/02/25/astro-stuff-galore-at-the-swap-and-sell.aspx">Astro stuff galore at the Swap and Sell</a></div></div><div class="column2"><h3>RECENT POSTS</h3><ul><li><a href="http://cs.astronomy.com/asy/b/daves-universe/archive/2019/01/15/brian-may-and-david-eicher-talks-in-london-bath-and-amsterdam.aspx">Brian May and David Eicher to give talks in London, Bath, and Amsterdam</a></li><li><a href="http://cs.astronomy.com/asy/b/daves-universe/archive/2019/01/09/lineup-for-2019-starmus-festival-announced.aspx">Starmus Festival&#39;s star-studded lineup for 2019 announced</a></li><li><a href="http://cs.astronomy.com/asy/b/astronomy/archive/2019/01/02/the-tucson-star-party-will-be-a-day-of-sun-and-stars.aspx">The Tucson Star Party will be a day of Sun and stars</a></li><li><a href="http://cs.astronomy.com/asy/b/daves-universe/archive/2019/01/01/new-horizons-39-first-look-at-ultima-thule-reveals-cosmic-bowling-pin.aspx">New Horizons&#39; first look at Ultima Thule reveals cosmic bowling pin</a></li><li><a href="http://cs.astronomy.com/asy/b/daves-universe/archive/2018/12/20/why-you-should-join-me-in-costa-rica.aspx">Why you should join me in Costa Rica</a></li><li><a href="http://cs.astronomy.com/asy/b/daves-universe/archive/2018/12/19/quot-new-horizons-quot-for-brian-may-with-new-release-of-solo-track.aspx">&quot;New Horizons&quot; for Brian May with new release of solo track</a></li></ul></div><div class="column3"><h3>TOPICS</h3><div class="left"><ul><li><a href="http://cs.astronomy.com/asy/b/astronomy/default.aspx">Local Group</a></li><li><a href="/community/from-the-industry">From the Industry</a></li></ul></div><div class="right"><ul><li><a href="http: